Have you heard of the Hermetic Principle of Correspondence? I'm sure you're aware of it, if only by other names, experiences and references. Such as "as above, so below" and "as within, so without; as without, so within." This principle refers to the concept that there are correspondences between the laws and phenomena of the various planes and realms; mental, spiritual, material as well as mineral, metallic, vegetable and animal, respectively. Harmony occurs when we actively seek the relationships between consciousness and matter. As we do so, we begin to uncover alchemical keys (often hidden in plain sight.) 

It is said that the Moon, la Luna, corresponds to the brain, Silver, Monday, and a keen perception of the layers of reality. 

This archetypal, alchemical awareness acts as an invitation; one layer, a foundation against which we can see other patterns emerge as we expand our consciousness through breath, sound and movement on Monday nights in Chakra Flow. 

